Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为爱丽丝游戏是应该一对一战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想和你或真红她们联手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我先说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会选择最切实的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到所有的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石好像去调查什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要出去一阵子  就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石她没有告诉你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的确这么说过的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一阵子就会有些寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  她很快就会回来的说哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且翠星石也会时不时地来喝茶的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石也这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「翠星石应该会常来玩的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是为了我这个老头子着想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石太狡猾了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己和老爷爷约好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一个人跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石想要一直和苍星石在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石不这么想的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石也有苍星石的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能就这样说没办法呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心翠星石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石昨天晚上也哭了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪把床单都弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了好多  好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓是个爱哭鬼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…金丝雀才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来看电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是清流素面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天到了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清流素面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午就来吃清流素面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么吃啊  也没有器具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那就流吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么纯  道具就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？真红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面很筋道  酱汁的香味也属上乘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是  很有夏日风情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大成功～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最辛苦的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！万岁！万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处收集塑料瓶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就接着流过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也多吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！我的功劳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没…没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的素面也可以再捡起来重新流过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我说  下一波就要过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饼干？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是糖哦  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的很好吃哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  也放点甜甜的煎蛋卷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石一定会喜欢的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来！别把奇怪的东西流过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是这样  一点都不知道收敛的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饼干和煎蛋卷怎么能放到水里流过去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来饼干就是直接吃比较好吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么还要放到水里流过去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候怎么会有食欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}给我等一下！喂！你们两个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我追上了吧  你们认命吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  别护着她们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什么「算了算了」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像苍星石对你来说是重要的人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于大家来说  你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这样不就不能让她们得到教训了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}姐姐你也太宠着她们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也不想勉强你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正是因为是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是吃一点比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下一波过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？粉色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——这个不是素面  是冷荞麦面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是清流素面了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种被背叛了的感觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么区别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  不过  冷荞麦面也很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～Delicious的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的面条有草莓的味道的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  草莓味！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪  纪  小雏也要粉色！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金也要吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕呀  粉色的只有一根而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦————？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不到9点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他真的是很累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠  翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…翠星石也有点困了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓也赶快去睡觉的说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了的说？真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那座房子通红的屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是很可爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是n之领域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  太奇怪了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户外面就直接连接着n之领域…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这一点的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真红  看那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们终于来了的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你想对我们做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦！什么也不想…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说好  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不想和你们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这里了还想装好孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你这一点了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想责怪你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想改变自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的献上你的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁要给你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就只有这样了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在爱丽丝游戏中所寻求的是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲大人所期盼的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问你自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人的愿望就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石的剪刀是为了保护人们的心灵而存在的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它并不适合用来伤害别人的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就跟着翠星石一起回去的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你的说  水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再继续这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太护着她了呢  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你妹妹好像并不希望这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍  苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人希望见到爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要回应他的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石只要和苍星石在一起就满足了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管能不能成为爱丽丝都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也很喜欢父亲大人的说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不要失去苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样你还要继续战斗的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先杀了翠星石的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  如果你妨碍我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一剪斩了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍…苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有这才能治愈父亲大人的悲痛的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要为他实现！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！振作点的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…又在哭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为苍星石太不孝顺了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为父亲大人在痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就情愿让姐姐哭泣的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…你已经有独自一人活下去的坚强了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去的说！苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…把…把我的…蔷薇圣母…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍…苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇圣母…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石…这就是爱丽丝游戏的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是父亲大人的愿望的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一切都开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不可能阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…翠星石要…翠星石要怎么办的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见
